Name: Description
COVID-19 Cases by Sex: Rates refer to the total number of confirmed COVID-19 cases per 100,000 individuals.

Name: Source Notes
COVID-19 Cases by Sex:
New York City Department of Health and Mental Hygiene, COVID-19 Data (2020). Retrieved from: https://github.com/nychealth/coronavirus-data

Data for COVID-19 Cases were updated weekly for the period of April 2, 2020 through April 2, 2021. These data are no longer being regularly updated. For the latest data on COVID-19, see: https://www1.nyc.gov/site/doh/covid/covid-19-data.page

Name: Notes
COVID-19 Cases by Sex: Data are cumulative and do not represent new cases per day listed. Data are being collected in real-time and are preliminary and subject to change as COVID-19 response continues. Due to delays in reporting, recent data are incomplete. Cases among transgender and gender nonconforming individuals are not included at this time.
